subject: Westminster Kennel Club Dog Show
Dogs
lead_paragraph: On Monday, a nearly 3-year-old, 15-inch-tall beagle named Uno took one small step toward the coveted title for his breed by winning the hound group, the first beagle to do so since 1939.
